{
  "stem": "293.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came over and almost kill me, and I stood-- stood up to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he became a friend, and he was giving me always a piece of bread or apple or something for Mila, you see?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were still together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in October 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then Mila said, Pol, get us on the list to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's your friend.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He did so much for you and for-- for the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe will put us on the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to the SS man whom I broke, Hans Schreiber, and I ask him to give my name and Mila's name to Mr.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schindler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Oskar Schindler, on his own, already put our name on the list.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we found out ourselves on the way to Brunnlitz, to the new factory-- But you didn't went directly to Brunnlitz right?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to Brunnlitz, but not directly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- the-- the men and women were separated. 900 men went to Gross-Rosen, and they stopped over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were stopped over there, and we were assured that we will-- never will see Oskar Schindler again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But about one week we spent there, and one day they give us a half bread-- half a loaf of bread, to every one of us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by list, they put us on the train to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Gross-Rosen?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Horrible condition.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For the whole week, first of all, we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we were-- there were no condition to sleep because in the barrack was about 900 people sleeping in the whole barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were sitting between the legs one after another like in a row, and we couldn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, They took everything and we got the stripe uniforms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my number is [NON ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It's branded in my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
